OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fand mostly cloudy, with a few isolated
OL,7,Fshowers, this evening. The cloud
OL,8,Fbreaking up to give occasional clear
OL,9,Fspells overnight. Breezy and mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry with bright or occasional
OL,12,Fsunny spells throughout the day. Cloud
OL,13,Fincreasing to bring some outbreaks of
OL,14,Flight showery rain by the evening.
OL,15,FFeeling warm in sunshine. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
