OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,6,Fdry with bright or sunny spells
OL,7,FSaturday and Sunday. Cloudier on
OL,8,FMonday with showers spreading inland
OL,9,Ffrom coastal areas. Feeling cooler,
OL,10,Fespecially along windward coastal
OL,11,Fdistricts.
